(making salty bets supersalty)
-------------------------------------------------------------

The extension that makes saltybets even more salty! ( http://www.saltybet.com/ )

To install go to chrome://extensions/ click "Load unpacked extension..."
and navigate to the folder the code is located in.

Probably lots of bugs, so enjoy.

At the moment we always bet on red for 50% of your current pot.

fair warning, the code will immedially start betting when able. 
(in other words, if you have a crazy amount of saltybucks don't use this)


